snippet.title: Ungate / The Survival Horror Game 2023 / Cinematic trailer
snippet.description:
Ungate / The Survival Horror Game 2023 / Cinematic trailer
Ungate is a survival horror game that will give you goosebumps along your way of trying to save your friends...
Steam release 5 Dec 2023: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2601620/Ungate/
Available now on Epic Games Store: https://launcher.store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/ungate-df09c8
Learn more at https://vivorlds.com/ungate
#new  #best #games #survival #ungate  #ungatechallenge #challenge  #horrorgaming  #challengeaccepted  #survivethedarkness


0:00 Intro
0:09 The beginning of the speech
0:14 Death is all you will find here
0:21 My people should have taken this world long ago
0:27 You will all burn 
0:31 Desperate breathing
0:35 Being attacked
0:38 Death is only the beginning
0:40 Running underground for your life
0:42 I am the fear of all mankind
0:46 Being attacked by swamp creatures
0:48 No one can stop me now
0:51 Scary storm at the surface
0:53 I will break you
0:56 Finding skulls underground
0:59 Nothing will save you
1:02 Dead zombies on the wall
1:04 I will be your nightmare
1:09 Being scared by a demon inside the house
1:11 You will scream
